&lt;a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%a5%9e%e7%a7%98%e5%8d%9a%e5%a3%ab-s5e10"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
Where do you think Van Gogh rates in the history of art?
&lt;p&gt;你认为梵高在艺术史上处于何等地位呢？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Well, big question.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;噢，这问题可不小。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But, to me, van Gogh is the finest painter of them all.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;但是，对我来说，梵高是史上最杰出的画家。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>